The original tags may not be attached. No more monthly dosing!\xe2\x80\xa2No potential for messy application issues and no need to isolate from children or other pets after treatment\xe2\x80\xa2Fewer doses mean fewer chances to miss a dose decreasing the likelihood of having gaps in protection\xe2\x80\xa2Dogs love the taste!How does Bravecto work:After giving your dog Bravecto, the medication quickly reaches tissue fluids under your dog's skin.\xc2\xa0When fleas and ticks feed on your dog, they ingest Bravecto and die.\xc2\xa0Bravecto kills fleas, prevents flea infestations and kills ticks (black-legged tick (a.k.a. deer tick),\xc2\xa0American dog tick, and brown dog tick) for 12 weeks.\xc2\xa0Bravecto also kills lone star ticks for 8 weeks.Flea Control Effectiveness with BravectoCautions:Not for human use. Keep this and all drugs out of the reach of children.Keep the product in the original packaging until use,in order to prevent children from getting direct access to the product.Do not eat, drink or smoke while handling the product.Wash hands thoroughly with soap and water immediately after use of the product.What is Bravecto used for:Bravecto kills adult fleas and is indicated for the treatment and prevention offlea infestations (Ctenocephalides felis), and the treatment and control of tick infestations[Ixodes scapularis (black-legged tick (a.k.a. deer tick)), Dermacentor variabilis (American dog tick),and Rhipicephalus sanguineus (brown dog tick)] for 12 weeks in dogs and\xc2\xa0puppies 6 months of age and older, and weighing 4.4 pounds or greater.Bravecto is also indicated for the treatment\xc2\xa0and control of Amblyomma americanum (lone star tick) infestations for 8 weeks in dogs andpuppies 6 months of age and older,\xc2\xa0and weighing 4.4 pounds or greater.Bravecto can be used in adult dogs, and it's even safe for use in breeding, pregnant, and lactating dogs.\xc2\xa0For use in growing puppies, they should be 6 months of age or older and weigh at least 4.4 lbs.How to administer Bravecto Chews for Dogs:Bravecto should be administered orally as a single dose every 12 weeks according tothe dosage schedule (How to Use tab)\xc2\xa0to provide a minimum dose of 11.4 aS"Silicon Stop Snoring Nose Clip Anti Snore Sleep Apnea Aid Device Night Tray\n>>Description\nDescriptionSnoring in general is caused by over-relaxation of the upper airway. Snoring always happens during less deep sleep. A normal and healthy sleep cycle should include aleast 25% at deep sleep, so not only are you disturbing your sleeping partner, you are also not getting the quality deep sleep that your body needs to rest and regenerate.This ingenious little device controls snoring when sleeping without interfering the normal sleep cycle.Avoids soft turbinate dropping and helps rest the tongue at normal position, thus opening up the nose cavity while breathing during sleep.Features*Effectively helps resolve mild to moderate snoring problems*No more sleepless night*Magnet insider the noseclip assists the elderly for normal nasal respiration/breathing*Made from quality silicone material*Comfortable and gently fits nostrils*Very easy to useEasy to clean*Come with a travel case for safe storage and easy carrying*Approx Size: 1.8cm x 1.5cm x 0.6cm*Color:TransparentHow to use the Anti Snoring Device:1.The anti snoring device will fit any shape of nostrils2.Place the protruding round tips towards the upper nostrils and place inwards3.Fits gently into nostrils, holding them wider apart and making breathing easier and quieter4.It is safe, convenient and reusable5.This product is made of high-tech 100% silicone gel6.It may take up to 3 days to a week to adapt to using the devicePackage includes1 x Clear Silicone Anti Snore Clip1 x Clear Carrying case\n>>Payment\nWe\xc2\xa0only\xc2\xa0accept\xc2\xa0payment\xc2\xa0through\xc2\xa0Paypal.\nIf\xc2\xa0you\xc2\xa0don't\xc2\xa0have\xc2\xa0Paypal\xc2\xa0account,\xc2\xa0please\xc2\xa0register\xc2\xa0at\xc2\xa0www.paypal.com.\nPayment\xc2\xa0must\xc2\xa0be\xc2\xa0received\xc2\xa0within\xc2\xa07\xc2\xa0days\xc2\xa0after\xc2\xa0auctions\xc2\xa0ended.\xc2\xa0Unpaid\xc2\xa0dispute\xc2\xa0will\xc2\xa0be\xc2\xa0filed\xc2\xa0to\xc2\xa0eBay\nfor\xc2\xa0the\xc2\xa0non\xc2\xa0payable\xc2\xa0bidders.\n>>Shipping\n1. aS"Original Sonoff B1 Led Bulb Dimmer Wifi Smart Light Bulbs Remote Control Wifi Light Switch Led Color Changing Light Bulb Works With AlexaDescriptionSonoff B1 is white and color ambiance dimmable LED bulb with E27 screw base.\xc2\xa0The dimming led lamp can be dimmed or brighten via iOS/Android App.\xc2\xa0With the App, users can select White, then the light will become white ambiance, they can set color temperature from cold to warm and change the brightness from 1%~100%.\xc2\xa0If they select color, they can change color spectrum of the RGB bulbs to favourite atmosphere.\xc2\xa0There are four available scenes for the dimming LED bulb: rest, reading, party and casual.\xc2\xa0The Sonoff B1 E27 color LED bulb is compatible with Amazon Alexa(Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Tap).\xc2\xa0Users can ask Alexa to dim or brighten, or adjust the colors of the led light bulb.Features- Remote ON/OFF- White & Color light- Color changeable- Color temperature adjusting- Dimmable brightness- Works with Nest- Works with Alexa- Works With Google Home- Just Add to your cart now.Specification Lamp Base: E27 Rated Power: 6W Typical Lumen Output: 600lm Beam Angle: 120 Degree typical Color Temperature: 2800K-6500K & RGB full color Dimmable: Yes (via app/Amazon Echo/Google Home) Wireless Standard: WiFi 2.4GHz Rated Input Voltage: 90-260V AC 50/60Hz Stand-by (Light off) power: 0.5W Max Operating Humidity: 5%~90% RH Operating Temperature: 0\xc2\xbaC~ 40\xc2\xbaC (32\xc2\xb0F ~ 104\xc2\xb0F ) Storage Temperature: -20\xc2\xbaC~ 80\xc2\xbaC (-4\xc2\xb0F ~ 176\xc2\xb0F )Main FunctionsNo Hub Required - Connect the bulb directly to your Wi-Fi at homeManage Remotely - Control your lights from anywhere with your tablet or smartphone the free eWeLink app (iOS, Android)Color Changing Hue - Fine-tune colors for every occasion and adjust brightness as well as light appearance from soft white (2800k) to daylight (6500k)Voice Control - Pair to Amazon Alexa and to enable voice controlCircadian Mode - Dynamically adjust light intensity and temperature to mimic natural light patternsSave Energy - Reduce energy use up to 80% without brightness or quality loss compared to a 60W incandescent bulbCompatibility - Compatible with Android, iOS and Amazon AlexaWorks With Alexa: \xc2\xa0 You can ask Alexa to change color temperature, color and brightness for Sonoff B1. \xc2\xa0 Color temperature mapping: \xc2\xa0 Shades of White Color Temperature value (in degrees Kelvin) warm, warm white 2200 incandescent, soft white 2700 white 4000 daylight, daylight white 5500 cool, cool white 7000 (if device can't support 7000k, then max supported CT will be used) Color temperature changing example: Note: you can only change this in White light, if the light is in Color mode, please switch to White in the App first. Alexa, change the {deviceName} to white Alexa, make the {deviceName} warm white Alexa, set the {deviceName} to daylight Alexa, set the {deviceName} cooler Alexa, make the {deviceName} whiter Alexa, set the {deviceName} softer Alexa, make the {deviceName} warmer \xc2\xa0 Color changing example: \xc2\xa0 Color words: red, yellow, green, blue, white, black, orange, pink, purple, gary, etc. Alexa, set the {deviceName} to red Alexa, change the {deviceName} to the color blue Alexa, turn the {deviceName} green \xc2\xa0 Brightness changing example: \xc2\xa0 Alexa, set {deviceName} to 90 percent Alexa, increase {deviceName} by 40 percent Alexa, decrease {deviceName} by 40 percent For more details, please read this blog. \xc2\xa0FAQ for Sonoff B1Read the detailed FAQ \xc2\xa0on Itead Smart Home Forum. If below answers can't solve your problem, please submit a feedback on eWeLink. 1. My device has added successfully but stays \xe2\x80\x9cOffline\xe2\x80\x9d. \xc2\xa0 Answers: The newly added device need 1-2 min to connect to your router and the Internet. If it stays offline for a long time, please judge the problem by the green led status: 1.1. Green led quickly blinks one time and repeats, which means device failed to connect to the router. The reason may be you have entered wrong WiFi password or your device is too far away from the router, which causes a weak WiFi signal. The device can not be added to the 5G-wifi-router, only the 2.4G-wifi is OK. At last, make sure that your router is MAC-open. \xc2\xa0 1.2. Green led slowly blinks one time and repeats, which means the device has connected to router and server but failed to be added to the device list. Then power on the device again, if it still not working, just add the device again. 1.3. Green led quickly blinks twice and repeats, this means the device has connected to the router but failed to connect to the server. Then please confirm your WiFi router works normally. 2. Why the APP can't find the device in pairing status? Answers: That's because of your phone's cache. Please close the WLAN of your phone then open it after a minute. At the same time, please power off the device if you can, then power up to try again. 3. My WiFi is expired, can I connect the devices to LAN? Can my phone be directly connected to device hotspot? For example, the management password is 6789, and then the number of 0*6789# will be valid after re-entering 1*6789#.3, Add opening password: press 0*1234#, then 2*opne password#, the password (4~6 digits), enter the command, add a set of open password, also can enter multiple sets of open password, such as open password#, to add more groups of password.4. Delete a set of open password: press 0*1234#, then enter the command with the 3*password#, and after deleting a set of passwords, you can also continuously enter: open password#, and delete multiple passwords.5. Delete all open passwords: delete all passwords by pressing 3*9*9#.See instructions for more details.Included:1 X Main Engine\xc2\xa010 X Promixity Card1 X User Manual2 X Screw1 X Connecting Linepictures\npaymentWe accept PayPal only.All major credit cards are accepted through secure payment processor PayPal.Payment must be received within 7 business days of auction closing.If you have bought multiple items from me, you can send me one payment for all the items instead of paying for them individually. aS'About UsContact UsPaymentShippingReturnsRadius - Source Toothbrush Replacement Heads Super Soft\n- 2 PackRadius Source Toothbrush Replacement Heads Super Soft 2 PackRadius\xc2\xa0Source Toothbrush\xc2\xa0Replacement Heads Super Soft 2 Pack\xc2\xa0boast\xc2\xa0their signature bed of super-soft, fanned bristles in a swappable pair. Switching one spent head for another instead of purchasing an entirely new toothbrush reduces plastic consumption and waste by 93%. Now that\xe2\x80\x99s something to smile about! Great for\xc2\xa0gums, the unique curved bristle-bed ensures our super-soft bristles clean and massage the gum rather than aggravating them. Featuring premium bristles that are made from 100% vegetable-based nylon to reduce our dependence on fossil fuels. The bristles are arranged in an elegant tanned shape, designed to gently yet throoughly clean and invigorate the entire mouth. Complete with a longer\xc2\xa0neck\xc2\xa0which allows for a better reach. A long, thin neck makes cleaning tricky-to-reach spots much easier, all the way to the very last molar!\xc2\xa0\xc2\xa0Great for Gums. 100% vegetable-based nylon\xc2\xa0to reduce reliance on fossil fuels. Longer neck for a better reach. Made in the USA, BPA-free, Vegan and Cruelty-free.Why Does BPA-Free Matter?Bisphenol A (commonly referred to as BPA)-is a carbon-based synthetic compound that interferes with your hormones in a detrimental way, and is proven to be particularly damaging to the health of babies and young children. In other words, BPA isn\'t something you want anywhere near your mouth, let alone your child\'s. And yet it\'s commonly found in hard plastics like those used to produce water bottles, food packaging and even your typical toothbrushes. Radius can assure you that their products do not contain BPA. Never have. Never will. And, on the subject of unnecessary nasties, Radius products are also free from latex, phthalate, glutens, and non-FDA-approved colors and dyes.Carefully Crafted by an Architect to be Better by DesignThe architects who designed the Radius range of toothbrushes are professional sticklers for elegant design. Their first (r)evolutionary product, the Radius Original, is now displayed at the Smithsonian Institute National Design Museum. From there, they expanded their products to encompass a range of personal care and travel essentials that combine function and beauty in just the same way.Just like other everyday products that have "evolved" through beautiful, functional design (think Dyson vacuum cleaners and Lumbar chairs), Radius products are totally unique. Each one is devised for a specialized purpose, utilizing different materials and one-of-a-kind manufacturing techniques-because refining and evolving the tools of your daily life is what they\'re all about.Radius-Green for the Right ReasonsRadius takes a holistic approach to designing and manufacturing their products, examining every step of the process-from prototyping and manufacturing to distribution and disposal-to ensure it\'s rooted in sustainable decisions that reduce their carbon footprint.Efficient ManufacturingManufacturing right here in the USA, in their own Radius factory, gives them complete control over production from start to finish, ensuring quality stays where they want it to be-the best of the best. They make, package and ship all their own products small batch-style on low-energy machines, recycling imperfect items and eliminating waste as much as possible. Materials are hand-selected to ensure that no heavy metals or carcinogenic substances find their way into the products. Primarily they use bioplastics, which are derived from renewable biomass sources (like vegetable oils and timber), agricultural byproducts, or even used plastic bottles. They\'re better for the environment, as well, requiring less fossil fuels and energy to produce (resulting in fewer greenhouse gases).In 2011, they took their environmentally conscious ethics to the next level-investing in 50,000 kilowatt solar collectors for their factory, which allow them to generate 67% of their electrical power from the sun.Lasting Longer Than the AverageRadius toothbrushes and products are designed to outlast most run-of-the-mill alternatives, thereby producing less waste. For instance, their Original toothbrush has 300% more bristles than an average toothbrush, making it effective for up to nine months compared to the average three months. The Source toothbrush, on the other other hand, allows the user to replace worn heads with a new one when necessary, eliminating the need to throw away and replace the entire brush. Their impressive longevity is due to a combination of hard-wearing materials and smart design, which prevents the bristles from wearing down so quickly. You save money, and together you and Radius help reduce energy consumption and waste in landfills by decreasing the need to manufacture more products.Back to the EarthWhat happens after a Radius design is spent is also a concern of theirs. The thought of their products and their packaging sitting in a landfill makes them cringe, which is why they always consider the end of a product\'s life before they begin making it. Not only do they re-purpose recycled materials to create their brushes, holders and cases, where possible they make them compostable, biodegradable and 100% recyclable, too.The Radius Story An unlikely beginning... Their story begins on the pristine sandy beaches of Tortola, British Virgin Islands, where the idea for their (r)evolutionary Radius Original was dreamed up by two architects with an insatiable love for clever design. Kevin Foley and James O\'Halloran believed even the most everyday products could be refined and improved, starting with the humble toothbrush.From their CEO Saskia Foley to the hard-working employees in their solar-powered factory, Radius is proudly women-owned and family-run. They thrive thanks to the team of dedicated, smart, close-knit individuals behind the scenes and value the contribution of each and every one of them. In fact, at Radius HQ, they\'re more like family than colleagues.Vegetable-based bristles reduce dependency on fossil fuels/petroleum.ABOUT USSHIPPINGPAYMENTRETURNSCONTACT USUntitled DocumentAbout UsFor\nthose leading active, healthful lives LuckyVitamin is the inspirational\nand supportive source for products and knowledge dedicated to helping everyone on their journey towards happy wellness.\nFor\nover three generations we have been dedicated to helping people lead\nhealthy lives.
